      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. specifically, how would u explain to the kids why some critics say this doctrine is basically just 'judicial activism' or that it's not actually written in the Constitution? i want to make sure they understand why it's such a controversial way to interpret the law.",
